.TH MILLENNIUM\-MCP 1 "July 2026" "millennium-helpers" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
millennium-mcp \- Model Context Protocol server for Millennium Helpers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B millennium-mcp
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Exposes Millennium helper commands as MCP tools for AI assistants
(Claude Desktop, Cursor, Windsurf, and similar clients).
.P
With no options, runs as a stdio JSON-RPC MCP server.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-register
Register the server in Claude Desktop, Windsurf, and Cursor config files
when those directories exist.
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-version
Show version information.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json
Claude Desktop MCP config (Linux).
.TP
.I ~/.cursor/mcp.json
Cursor MCP config.
.TP
.I ~/.codeium/windsurf/mcp_config.json
Windsurf MCP config.
.SH SEE ALSO
Full tool list and setup:
.I docs/mcp.md
in the millennium-helpers repository.
.P
.BR millennium-diag (1),
.BR millennium-upgrade (1),
.BR millennium-theme (1)
